reviews.review_text: Ive been coming to the A&W on E Broadway for a while after shift and Sampan always welcomes me with a smile and is very attentive. He makes my experience at this location very pleasant and deserve a raise for his humble nature about the way he goes about getting his work done.

I go there often and Im always received with a big smile and a friendly greeting from the staff. They put close attention to the details of my order and its always accurate. I really special thanks to the lovely lady prepping the food, whos super friendly and a huge gratitude cheer to the whole staff whos always attentive and does a terrific job every single day.

Delicious Food     ...A&W has been an Excellent, Phenomenal, Amazing, Awesome Eating & Drinking Experience... I LOVE Teen Burgers, Fries  , Onion Rings, Hot Dogs, Root Beer  , Apple   Turnovers, Buddy Burgers with Cheese, And The Entire Menu @ This Fine Establishment!!!!!!!

The burger was yummy, the water in the glass mug was chilled, and the place was clean. The customer ahead of me was an older lady who had trouble speaking loudly, and the person taking the order was very patient and helped get an answer to what the lady wanted to get. Dietary restrictions: I ask for no cheese as it is dairy, and the rest of the Teen Burger is dairy free. I opt to take off the A&W seasoning and pickles to reduce the overall number of ingredients by a lot. I think the rest of the burger speaks for itself well!
One of the most kind and helpful customer service. Super nice staff specially Jeel who took my order and suggested lot of good things from the menu.

Hello A&W team, I am really glad to have lunch at your restaurant because of many things like the guest service i am getting from the guy in the front counter was awesome and it feel like really appreciate to me and also the atmosphere they all create . Thank you A&W
Place is clean, staff is attentive (especially little indian girl at counter, dont know her name). Food is served fast. Toilets are free to use even for non-customer.

Im deeply satisfied with the food. I specially asked for some customisation, Amanpreet stepped up and delivered with utmost care respecting my allergies. In my entire life I have never encountered such an experience. It was heartwarming to see that there are still people out there who knows how to deliver, serve and be a human being!! Mostly you will find such fast food outlets throwing food on your faces but I can guarantee not here. It s worth every penny here. Thanks Amanpreet.

Cashier was great! She answered all my questions and gave suggestions. Will come back here. By the way, if you order the kids meal they also have made Good snacks (esp for kids with sensitivities).way to go!

Every five days in a week I go to this A&W for my morning coffee and I am loved with the brewed coffee and also i found a guys who is skinny and tall work in front is professionally trained to deal with customer always smiling.
This is actually a very good, clean A&W. Staff is always friendly and hard working.
Although it was extremely hot inside last time I have been there, the customer service is great!
I tasted the Beyond Meat Burger yesterday, it was delicious! The services was also good. Will try another beyond meat products next time.

I love this place , very professional ans make tasty burgers. Especially Manju   , my favourite out of all. She made so tasty burgers , puts so much love and everything that she make is so even and clean and balanced. Because of her i keep coming at this site .
Fresh food with great customer service. Nice and clean store.

I give this place 5 stars because, as fast food goes, this gives it all. I understood the menu, I placed my order easily, I sat at a clean table, my food was ready in reasonable time, I ate in peace, the burger, yam fries and root beer all tasted as they should. What more can you expect?

The young man at the front counter tonight tall slim good looking young man extremely professional I was very very very specific with what I wanted I requested special items the young man listened the man provided everything with a smile and served me like I was a king this man is extremely well trained I do not know his name although I do understand that he speaks Hindi this man was working tonight it s approximately 1030 and this was at the commercial Broadway store why there is a such a low level customer service rating I am very surprised all of the employees were busy nobody was fooling around and everybody was serious thank you for an absolute delicious meal I have not eaten a burger in years thank you thank you and thank you
It was good service and their beyond meat burger is always good and one of the reason to choose it over McDonald s.

I LOVE A&W Root beer, its the BEST Root beer ever. Its smooth clean taste makes for an awesome drink, standing on its own merit or mixed into it a scoop or two of vanilla ice cream for an outstanding Root beer float! Then theres the burgers made fresh and just to your own personal taste. Toppings added are up to you and theyve got a whole slew of them, all kept clean and fresh awaiting to be added to your freshly made burger, what else could you ask for in a fast food restaurant hey!? In my opinion, you cant ever go wrong with the choice to visit your local A&W Canada so go now and eat up the A&W arsenal one burger at a time!
Loved the vegan options. Wish the beyond burger came with a vegan cheez substitute, but was good nonetheless.
Wonderful staff. Very courteous. Always smiling

I prefer this morning breakfast over any other fast food chain. Mcdonalds can be over rated however they have only the best price. I would be all over this place if they have better coupons. My top 5 fastfood chain. 1. Wendys 2. Aw 3. Churchies chicken 4. Carls junior 5. Burger king. I know we all love our fastfood.  Go aw sausage bacon egger

My friend and I came to A&W 4 minutes before close tonight  (August 22) we didnt really expect to be served so close to close but not only did the gentleman serving us enthusiasticly reassure us that we could order whatever we liked, he was friendly, warm and professional throughout out interation. We didnt get his name but I really hope this company aknowlages its dedicated staff because he really made us feel welcome and taken care of. The food was tasty and hit the spot just right so props to the cooks too
Loved this location. FAST service, friendly staff, and I even managed to get a table to eat - so the burger and fries were really fresh. Tasted delicious.

In my opinion, A&W is an excellent fast food place to go to. Their burgers and fries are some of the best Ive had in my life, as they do not use nearly as many preservatives in their food as opposed to McDonalds, allowing you to enjoy the taste of real food. Their breakfasts are wonderful too, and their coffee is only second to Starbucks.

This little corner restaurant, being at a SkyTrain station, saw a lot of traffic even at night. The main cashier handled people very well with various requests in addition to food orders. The place was mostly clean, all dishes were put away regularly.
Nov. 4 2022 UPDATE: Things have improved massively! ORIGINAL: Didnt allow washroom use, departure from previously excellent customer service
reviews.response_from_owner_text: We are sorry to hear this, Kaylan. We ll make sure to share your feedback with the team. We hope you ll give us  the opportunity to serve you again.

reviews.review_text: I really like this place  of all the burger fast food joints A&W has got to be the best one lets put it this way root beer float in an actual mug that you can purchase if you like or not cause  thats just how they roll not to mention they have been in the burger game for as long as I can remember anybody who is a burger connoisseur has to eat here the staff are courteous wich makes all the difference whether you dine in or take out  you will want to come back

Been going to the same A & W for the last 6 or 7 months, same breakfast (all canadian) every single time. The staff atcthis bramch are amazing, very nice polite and helpful. Will keep coming here till the foreseeable future lol!

Realpromovers.com and the Real Pro Movers Moving company of Vancouver B.C. love A&W! The poutine is the best of all the top fast food joints - hands down. Fresh - delicious - flavorful feasts! Also thanks for the quick service as well. See you next time :)
i tend to go here after work when i need a quick snack before going home, always yummy and it s consistently clean here. i m so glad it s open late, and there is great social distancing organization!
Gave me change for my $20

Staff was great,I only go a couple times a month but was recognized and the staff member knew my order from my past. Food was great!!. Ill put your poutine up against anyone.. Thank you!! Awesome job!!

Better than McDonalds, thats fosho.  Download the app to get good deals and coupons. Mozza will always be my fav.  Poutine or sweet potato fries are a must as well
Its a nice place ,clean environment ,staff was nice and helpful, service was quick. What more can you ask for in a fast food place?
The staff were great honestly probably should have been asked  to go since all I was doing was writing

Fast, friendly, service, by these young hardworking youngsters, and always done with a smile, as well.  No matter which location!  And, we have soon discovered by ourselves.  That it is the smile, that counts the most.  Keep, up the great work, A&W!   :)
Very clean and hygienic place. I ordered my fav Veg deluxe beyond meat burger and it made my day! Was soooo yummyyyyyy!! Highly recommend this place
Friendly staffs. They let me in and wait inside after hours. Offer me drinks.  Working hard. Thanks and keep up the good work!
I had a great experience as my food was great. The fries were hot and the beyond burger was delicious. Thanks you guys
Great Service .Nice girls / boys attendents  Always  fresh and hot food.They did nt discriminate me as i am also from same community which they from.
Walked in the place was empty a beautiful person named Jenny smiling and asking me what I would like made me smile and happy myself
I tried the beyond meat burger... truest loved it. You could not tell it wasn t a meat patty... root beer came in a really frosty glass.
Really friendly staff and was super fast to get my food. Appreciated the service
Always love A&W motsa burger in a lettuce wrap, and safe for people with Celiac Disease.
Good food and great customer service provided by this A&W and their staff. Really appreciated.
Good food, 24/7 breakfast, lunch and dinner. This place is my go-to for delivery.
Its really good, Manpreet was so nice :) and the Sweet potato chips was great!
Loved this place. Wish Id had the time and the stomach to try everything while I was there. Come to Australia please!
PSoved the food as aways Im a pretty chubby guy who I say Im Fluffy and a clown to be around.
Really like the burgers but the Apple Pecan Chicken Salad is THE BEST!
Clean, friendly service. Eat here often, yet to have anything taste off.
Very clean place, especially considering the area and the manager working that night was very accommodating.
A&W always offers good food and I can always rely on getting a good burger no matter the location! Stay awesome A&W!
Great fast food place always busy but quick
This is a fantastic place to grab some food on the go.  Quick and friendly service.
I had great experience there. Food was really good.
Had the new Nashville chicken burger and it was excellent..tasted so yummy
I have always loved A&W, great burgers and the root beer is phenomenal.
Pretty good. Better than McDonalds for sure.
Great burgers, terrific location, efficient and friendly staff.
High quality fast burger joint that has embraced the excellent tasting beyond meat burger.
Standard A&W food wise. Quick and friendly service from staff.
Food was fast and warm. Good eats.
I love A&W and their beyond meat burger is my new favorite thing!
Friendly staff and food was made fast.
these people are fast , friendly and fresh food!
has anyone anywhere had bad a&w? dont worry I wait....
All of the food is great, nice and fresh, not processed
